manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

playstore_details.title: Nocrop Photo Editor: Filters, Effects, Pic Collage
playstore_details.description:
Nocrop Photo Editor is a powerful and free photo editor and camera app. One-tap features help you to easily add stunning filters, effects and stickers. Easy-to-use  blur option, no crop needed to resize your image into 1:1 size for Instagram, Snapchat, Tik Tok, Facebook, Whatsapp, etc. Amazing collage maker presents you easy layouts to make photo collage. All these awesome editing tools are 100% free!

Superb features of the Nocrop photo editor

👑 Nocrop provides you the essential picture editing tools to make your pics fabulous. Use the pro camera to take a selfie and start editing!

🎁 Fascinating pic collage tool helps you to create collages with 100+ grids, massive backgrounds, and frames. You can add up to 15 photos to remix your collection into a beautiful photo grid. You can also start from scratch and freestyle your photo collage. 

🎉 You need no crop to blur background with stunning DSLR blur effect. Easy-to-use interface helps you no crop easily.

💍 Nocrop presents you hundreds of different fonts and text to choose from so you can add texts to your pics. Determine the font that reflects your style and generate your own incredible artwork!

💖 Photo blender and light fx effects can revolutionize your photos with one click. Apply the filter you want and edit them into marvelous images. Dozens of awesome filters such as glitch, neon, retouch, etc. are waiting for you to build your masterpiece in Nocrop. If you like oldies but goldies choose from vintage, retro, sparkle filters.

🍫 Nocrop offers you a vast library of fun stickers to select from. Adorn your photos with cartoons, doodles, and cute emojis. Create memes to have fun with your friends. We update our stickers and emoji library regularly for special days such as; halloween, Valentine's Day, Christmas, etc.

🎆 Stylize a scrapbook of your memories with the help of Nocrop which will prove your photography skills to be extraordinary to your social media followers. Get ready to be asked, if you have used photoshop :)

🎭 Share your artwork, drawing, selfie instantly on social platforms such as Instagram, Facebook, Whatsapp, Snapchat, Tik Tok, VK, Tumblr, Flickr, Twitter and Pinterest.

🔥 Don’t forget Nocrop Photo Editor: Filters, Effects, Neon Sketch is a completely free pics editor to design wonderful artworks!
